\": { \"enabled\": false },\n      \"wacli\": { \"enabled\": false },\n      \"xurl\": { \"enabled\": false },\n      \"feishu-task\": { \"enabled\": true },\n      \"gh-issues\": { \"enabled\": false },\n      \"github\": { \"enabled\": false },\n      \"tmux\": { \"enabled\": false }\n    }\n  },\n  \"update\": {\n    \"checkOnStart\": false\n  },\n  \"plugins\": {\n    \"allow\": [\n      \"feishu-openclaw-plugin\",\n      \"feishu-greeting\",\n      \"miaoda-keepalive\"\n    ],\n    \"entries\": {\n      \"feishu\": {\n        \"enabled\": false\n      },\n      \"feishu-openclaw-plugin\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      },\n      \"feishu-greeting\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"config\": {\n          \"message\": \"👋 Hi，我是**姚霖的助手**，一只生活在飞书里的 🦞 小龙虾，我已准备就绪，并学习了[如何使用飞书](https://bytedance.larkoffice.com/docx/MFK7dDFLFoVlOGxWCv5cTXKmnMh)，有什么需要帮忙的随时说~\",\n          \"targets\": [\"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\"]\n        }\n      },\n      \"miaoda-keepalive\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"config\": {}\n      }\n    },\n    \"installs\": {\n      \"feishu-openclaw-plugin\": {\n        \"source\": \"npm\",\n        \"spec\": \"@larksuiteoapi/feishu-openclaw-plugin\",\n        \"installPath\": \"./extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin\",\n        \"version\": \"2026.3.8-beta.0\"\n      },\n      \"feishu-greeting\": {\n        \"source\": \"path\",\n        \"installPath\": \"./extensions/feishu-greeting\"\n      },\n      \"miaoda-keepalive\": {\n        \"source\": \"path\",\n        \"installPath\": \"./extensions/miaoda-keepalive\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}","cwd":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773293026475}}
{"type":"message","id":"3545c715","parentId":"371b5cd3","timestamp":"2026-03-12T05:24:07.442Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到了 tools 部分，有 `feishu_search_user` 工具，这正是我使用的工具。从配置看，工具本身是允许的（在 deny 列表中没有排除）。\n\n问题可能出在：\n1. 飞书应用本身的权限（需要在飞书开放平台配置）\n2. 用户 OAuth 授权的范围\n\n让我检查一下飞书应用是否需要特殊的通讯录权限。在飞书开放平台，需要配置通讯录权限作用域才能访问完整的组织架构。\n\n让我看看飞书相关的 skill 或者文档，看看是否有更多信息。\n\n实际上，我应该直接告诉用户：问题可能在于飞书应用的通讯录权限没有在开放平台配置。飞书搜索用户这个工具依赖的是应用权限，如果应用没有配置\"通讯录只读\"权限，就无法搜索到所有员工。\n\n用户可能需要在飞书开放平台给应用添加通讯录相关的权限 scope。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我查了一下配置，工具本身没有被禁用。\n\n**问题根源**：飞书应用权限需要在 **飞书开放平台** 配置。\n\n`feishu_search_user` 工具依赖飞书应用的通讯录权限Scope。如果应用没有开通相应权限，就无法搜到全部员工。\n\n**需要的权限**：\n- `contact:user.base:readonly` - 读取用户基本信息\n- `contact:user.id:readonly` - 读取用户 user_id\n- `contact:department.base:readonly` - 读取部门基本信息\n\n**解决方法**：\n1. 登录飞书开放平台：https://open.feishu.cn/\n2. 进入您的应用（App ID: cli_a938f637ab391bd2）\n3. 在「权限管理」中添加通讯录相关权限\n4. 重新发布应用\n\n您可以去检查一下应用的权限配置，看看通讯录权限是否已开通。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":1606,"output":358,"cacheRead":46682,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48646,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773293026481}}
{"type":"message","id":"30bc2c8d","parentId":"3545c715","timestamp":"2026-03-12T05:24:10.706Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /home/gem/workspace/agent/media/inbound/51fa5889-945a-4bc2-9cc9-4adc0c95f24d.jpg (image/jpeg) | /home/gem/workspace/agent/media/inbound/51fa5889-945a-4bc2-9cc9-4adc0c95f24d.jpg]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nSystem: [2026-03-12 13:24:08 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b [msg:om_x100b5410932ce0acc3fdd4f371884d2, image, 1 attachment(s)]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5410932ce0acc3fdd4f371884d2\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-03-12 13:24 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\"\n}\n```\n\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/media/inbound/51fa5889-945a-4bc2-9cc9-4adc0c95f24d.jpg"}],"timestamp":1773293050701}}
