{"type":"message","id":"e6557665","parentId":"9c80eea1","timestamp":"2026-03-12T05:45:10.876Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"还是失败了。让我看看feishu渠道的配置。看起来机器人身份发消息可能有限制，或者需要不同的参数。让我看看error是什么或者换一种方式。\n\n实际上，根据 feishu-channel-rules skill 的说明，在 Lark conversations 中消息默认以机器人身份发送。但现在私聊发给其他用户可能有限制。\n\n让我看看 feishu-im-read skill 中有没有关于发消息的说明，或者检查下配置。\n\n先检查下问题，可能需要检查 openclaw 配置或者查看具体的错误信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_44shzlbx3hvo_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/gem/workspace/agent/openclaw.json | grep -A 30 '\"feishu\"'"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":101,"output":148,"cacheRead":54269,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54518,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773294303009}}
