{"type":"message","id":"84a6fe8c","parentId":"c7016277","timestamp":"2026-03-12T05:46:05.741Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我开启权限。但我之前说过，我没有办法直接去飞书开放平台开启权限。我需要再次向用户解释这一点。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n抱歉，我无法直接在飞书开放平台上操作，需要您手动开启：\n\n**操作步骤**：\n1. 打开 https://open.feishu.cn/\n2. 登录管理员账号\n3. 进入「应用管理」→ 找到应用 `cli_a938f637ab391bd2`\n4. 点击「权限管理」\n5. 搜索添加：`im:message:send_as_bot`\n6. 发布应用\n\n您完成授权后告诉我，我再试着用机器人身份发消息。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":52719,"output":130,"cacheRead":2596,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55445,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773294357782}}
