{"type":"message","id":"aa0ae39f","parentId":"4a47feb1","timestamp":"2026-03-12T09:08:40.176Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"浏览器不可用。我无法直接打开飞书任务应用。让我请用户截图飞书任务应用中的全员任务情况。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n抱歉，浏览器工具不可用，我无法直接打开飞书任务应用。\n\n请您打开飞书「任务」应用，截图全员任务列表发给我，我帮您整理成表格。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":198,"output":66,"cacheRead":65789,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66053,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773306515338}}
{"type":"message","id":"9532f340","parentId":"aa0ae39f","timestamp":"2026-03-12T09:10:13.347Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-12 17:10:12 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b [msg:om_x100b541c618e9400c2bf54826cd5109]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b541c618e9400c2bf54826cd5109\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-03-12 17:10 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\"\n}\n```\n\n我们公司都有哪些员工"}],"timestamp":1773306613341}}
{"type":"message","id":"23263e9a","parentId":"9532f340","timestamp":"2026-03-12T09:10:23.824Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户再次问这个问题。之前我已经通过截图识别了营销部的员工，但用户说行政部还有很多人。让我尝试用图像理解来查看用户可能发来的截图。但用户这次没有发截图，只是问问题。\n\n我应该告诉用户之前通过截图识别到的信息，并请用户继续提供其他部门的截图。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"根据之前营销部截图识别，公司员工包括：\n\n| 姓名 | 职位 | 部门 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 姚霖 | 总经理 | 营销部 |\n| 何杰 | 副总经理 | 营销部 |\n| 王垣皓 | 销售顾问 | 营销部 |\n| 李文娅 | 商务经理 | 营销部 |\n| 郝彦艳 | 售前经理 | 营销部 |\n| 王文强 | 销售顾问 | 营销部 |\n| 范景昊 | 销售顾问 | 营销部 |\n\n加上之前搜索到的：\n- 刘晓（培训部）\n- 刘世龙（服务部）\n\n**其他部门（行政部、培训部、产品部、服务部等）**请您截图发给我，我继续识别补充完整。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":470,"output":229,"cacheRead":65789,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66488,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773306613343}}
