{"type":"message","id":"e9a97335","parentId":"9a015939","timestamp":"2026-03-12T09:13:32.515Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"要具备完整通讯录查询能力，需要在飞书开放平台开启以下权限：\n\n**通讯录权限**：\n- `contact:user.base:readonly` - 读取用户基本信息\n- `contact:user.id:readonly` - 读取用户 ID\n- `contact:department.base:readonly` - 读取部门信息\n- `contact:department.id:readonly` - 读取部门 ID\n- `contact:user.search:readonly` - 搜索用户\n\n**操作步骤**：\n1. 打开 https://open.feishu.cn/\n2. 进入应用 `cli_a938f637ab391bd2`\n3. 点击「权限管理」→「添加权限」\n4. 搜索并添加上述权限\n5. 发布应用\n\n**为什么搜索不到所有人？**\n- 飞书 API 需要关键词匹配才能搜索\n- 无权限时搜索范围受限\n- 开通权限后可以搜索更完整的信息\n\n您开通权限后告诉我，我再帮您查询完整通讯录。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":53429,"output":212,"cacheRead":13941,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67582,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773306747368}}
