{"type":"message","id":"b13fb8d3","parentId":"5d7509be","timestamp":"2026-03-12T15:03:02.866Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_zcsdeilv6aku_1","toolName":"feishu_im_user_get_messages","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54110da094a0b3c7851c8fc7ab1\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"🦞 大家好，我是姚总的AI助理！\\n【自我介绍】\\n我是基于 OpenClaw 框架开发的智能助手，主要能力包括：\\n【底层技术】\\n• OpenClaw - 开源 AI Agent 框架\\n• 飞书开放平台 API - 集成飞书生态\\n• 大语言模型 - 理解与生成能力\\n• 浏览器自动化 - Web 操作能力\\n• 文档处理 - PDF/Word/Excel 解析\\n【工作能力】\\n📄 文档撰写与整理\\n📊 数据表格处理\\n📅 日程管理与会议安排\\n🔍 信息搜索与整理\\n💬 消息沟通与协调\\n以后有什么需要帮忙的随时找我~\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a938f637ab391bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-12T13:50:47+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b541173b3d4bcc10d40f590af620\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"system\",\n      \"content\": \"姚霖 invited 姚霖的助手 to this group. New members can view messages sent after they joined.\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-12T13:49:11+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55c8fc2528b8c3a972302d9e08e\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@_all  2月工资条已发放，若有问题，请在今天17点前反馈，谢谢！\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_2c47b54a9dbdbd13729a411a625283a1\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"刘晓\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-10T15:41:34+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b579942d33cb4c37c136d39c56f1\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@_all  1月工资条已发放，若有问题，请在今天16点前反馈，谢谢！\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_2c47b54a9dbdbd13729a411a625283a1\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"刘晓\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-02-10T14:31:30+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b576e98ff6c8cc4dd016d2e9b3df\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"![image](img_v3_02ul_9be9efb6-1aa5-4c13-971a-1cbb8cf6e2bg)\\nOKR填写完成之后需要发起上级确认操作，完成上级确认后才算填写成功。\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"姚霖\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-02-06T16:59:15+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b570527f548b4c44dc9af7b8e730\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"image\",\n      \"content\": \"![image](img_v3_02uj_cc34ede2-ea3d-4a15-a187-408ee62e33bg)\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_2c47b54a9dbdbd13729a411a625283a1\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"刘晓\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-02-04T17:51:15+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5705262e9470c108c4bf894b743\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"Hello，小伙伴们：\\n[巳巳如意]蛇舞旧岁留佳绩，[一马当先]马踏新春启华章\\n值此辞旧迎新之际，为全体同事度过一个平安祥和的春节假期，结合公司运营实际，现将2026年春节放假相关事宜通知如下：\\n\\n⏰放假时间：\\n2026年 2月14日至2月24日，共计11天；\\n2026年2月25日(初九)开工，2月28日上班。\\n\\n💓温馨提示：\\n1、请大家提前梳理手头工作，完成节前收尾工作；\\n2、放假前请务必做好办公区域安全检查：关闭电脑、空调、打印机、插座等设备电源；\\n3、假期出行注意人身财产安全，确保平安返程。\\n[福]旧岁耕耘结硕果，新年奋进续新篇[福]祝愿2026年大家马到功成开新局，聚力同心赢未来，愿我们步履铿锵，共赢锦绣前程[烟花]@_all\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_2c47b54a9dbdbd13729a411a625283a1\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"刘晓\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-02-04T17:51:10+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b571a96b358acc1418cc2f42bab8\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"![image](img_v3_02uj_145a5886-064f-418e-9b5a-f44c020b2c9g)\\n@所有人 以后所有通知回复不用回复收到，点击拇指图标，选择OK即可；移动端操作长按消息，选择OK即可。\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"姚霖\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-02-04T14:56:08+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b58f025453898b4c1a78832dae4d\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"收到\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_0a41155c9f7ed341a3c314470ad4768c\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王垣皓\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-01-30T13:50:48+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b58f028b898b0b32898715cda05a\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"收到\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_a1fccaba597ded53dd8e0bb421fbb7a1\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"刘世龙\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-01-30T13:49:27+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    }\n  ],\n  \"has_more\": true,\n  \"page_token\": \"4cXSlmN7uFAnWWU5yfIGMJ-W_SjfRKLAvsCfB8YQtVogkuV-9M9hd5GgaqYZWyVjPlzh-BOP4wyj38wToCzx1t09yhhXuQLAsHQuyz2Z2aZjApyU-wEotlDiOdOkNi3B\"\n}"}],"details":{"messages":[{"message_id":"om_x100b54110da094a0b3c7851c8fc7ab1","msg_type":"post","content":"🦞 大家好，我是姚总的AI助理！\n【自我介绍】\n我是基于 OpenClaw 框架开发的智能助手，主要能力包括：\n【底层技术】\n• OpenClaw - 开源 AI Agent 框架\n• 飞书开放平台 API - 集成飞书生态\n• 大语言模型 - 理解与生成能力\n• 浏览器自动化 - Web 操作能力\n• 文档处理 - PDF/Word/Excel 解析\n【工作能力】\n📄 文档撰写与整理\n📊 数据表格处理\n📅 日程管理与会议安排\n🔍 信息搜索与整理\n💬 消息沟通与协调\n以后有什么需要帮忙的随时找我~","sender":{"id":"cli_a938f637ab391bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-12T13:50:47+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false},{"message_id":"om_x100b541173b3d4bcc10d40f590af620","msg_type":"system","content":"姚霖 invited 姚霖的助手 to this group. New members can view messages s