{"type":"message","id":"4031beef","parentId":"a77286e1","timestamp":"2026-03-12T15:28:25.223Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问有没有插件可以解决消息已读状态的问题。让我想想飞书开放平台有没有相关的 API 和权限。\n\n飞书确实有获取消息已读状态的 API，需要以下权限：\n- `im:message.read_users_readed` - 读取消息已读用户\n\n让我建议用户去开通这个权限。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"可以通过飞书开放平台权限解决：\n\n**需要的权限**：\n- `im:message.read_users_readed` - 读取消息已读人员列表\n\n**操作步骤**：\n1. 打开 https://open.feishu.cn/\n2. 进入应用 `cli_a938f637ab391bd2`\n3. 权限管理 → 添加权限 → 搜索 `im:message.read_users_readed`\n4. 发布应用\n\n开通后我可以帮您查询消息的已读/未读人员名单。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":75038,"output":173,"cacheRead":2557,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77768,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773329297023}}
